def str2float(string):
    try:
        return float(string)
    except:
        return 0.0
df['Time']= df['Time'].apply(str2float)

# 把时间表示从秒转换成分钟
def second2minute(second):
    try:
        return int(float(second)/60)
    except:
        return 0

df['Time'] = df['Time'].apply(second2minute)
df

# 统计每分钟内的弹幕数量
count = df.groupby(['Time'],as_index=False)['Time'].agg({'cnt':'count'})

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib inline

plt.rcParams['font.sans-serif']=['KaiTi']
danmudf = df.groupby('Time').agg({'Text':['count']})
danmudf.plot(kind='line', figsize=(20, 10), legend=False)
plt.title("vlog弹幕趋势图", fontweight='bold', fontsize=25)
plt.xlabel('时间点', fontweight='bold', fontsize=20)
plt.ylabel('弹幕量', fontweight='bold', fontsize=20, rotation=0)
plt.show()
